<div class="fullscreen-card fullscreen-card--center" style="padding:20px;">
    <h2> This milestone is missing in {{card.repo.data.repo.full_name}}</h2>
    <div class="well">
    <p>
      You are attempting to assign an issue from {{card.repo.data.repo.full_name}} into a milestone that exists in {{column.milestone.repo.data.repo.full_name}}. HuBoard can merge milestones across your linked repositories as long as the titles are the same. 

    </p>
    <p>
    Click the create button to copy this milestone into {{card.repo.data.repo.full_name}} with the title <strong> {{column.title}} </strong>
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="flex-form-top">
    <button class="hb-button" disabled={{disabled}} {{action 'createTheMilestone' }}> Create it for me </button> or <a {{action 'closeModal'}} href="#">Cancel</a>
  </div>
</div>
